{"tid":1534462,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"大家應諗諗而家應該點做","createTime":"2019-09-03T04:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:29.000Z","uid":170601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"33c9b3329c3bb0faefecd389d4240b0a87779579","tid":1534462,"uid":170601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"其實而家林狗採用拖字決，<br />\n又不出解放軍，又不戒嚴，又不實行緊急法，<br />\n大家應諗諗下一步點做，<br />\n應該減少被捕來同佢玩鬥拖"},{"pid":"28644a8b52356d369569a7d11ae41fb9e3204124","tid":1534462,"uid":38494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:16:03.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">出糧換美金  全民提款日</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.07 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.08 美國人權及民主法案大遊行 14:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.13 各區同慶賀中秋 人鏈 19:00 - 22:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">9.14 機場交通測試 13:00</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">轉頭見</span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></div>"},{"pid":"a1960d868ee50db844021bc415072c2a85f3d88f","tid":1534462,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:16:35.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a00c7a00a53e537671fb3009e35e559353dedf0e","tid":1534462,"uid":285855,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:18:01.000Z","msg":"香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還成10萬億美金<br />\n佢話前朝唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還唔認點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n如果借據美國買左我地係美殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=8a571a30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=27779150\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7RnZZ8.png&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFBSGsERVwMiaoyLN1PNQjS0%3D&h=44547c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png</a>"},{"pid":"c1acaddc8a1ed17fe28b461ca63b72398a0aac94","tid":1534462,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:19:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得我地要和平地渡過呢段時間，直到我地部署好下一步大型既國際宣傳運動<br />\n除非我地組織到過百以上既靈魂打返d狗轉頭做破窗效應，但好難"},{"pid":"d8a983f7838004f0a4042b99f4a80c0606f08984","tid":1534462,"uid":34927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:22:00.000Z","msg":"中共係至撚無賴，鬥無賴係唔會贏<br />\n但我地可以帶起一d運動係大眾受益，全民唔交稅，打爆港鐵閘機，打爆隧道收費亭"},{"pid":"93d366bbd4d1fb491bb873a4f53e6b2b0cc8c48b","tid":1534462,"uid":269512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33c9b3329c3bb0faefecd389d4240b0a87779579","tid":1534462,"uid":170601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:14:22.000Z","msg":"其實而家林狗採用拖字決，<br />\n又不出解放軍，又不戒嚴，又不實行緊急法，<br />\n大家應諗諗下一步點做，<br />\n應該減少被捕來同佢玩鬥拖"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T04:33:29.000Z","msg":"等候時機，時間在正義一方。"}]}